1
00:00:01,330 --> 00:00:03,460
I ended up waking you up anyway.

2
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:08,300
Don't worry about it. I'm the one
who showed up unannounced yesterday.

3
00:00:10,140 --> 00:00:12,300
Just leave the key in the mailbox.

4
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:13,600
Take your time.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,720
Okay.

6
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:16,980
Well, I'm off!

7
00:00:19,640 --> 00:00:21,020
I'm heading out.

8
00:00:21,230 --> 00:00:22,400
Have a good day.

9
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:23,650
Take care.

10
00:00:24,520 --> 00:00:25,780
Yeah.

11
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:27,440
What is it?

12
00:00:30,820 --> 00:00:32,200
What you just said...

13
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:33,950
Could you say it again?

14
00:00:34,910 --> 00:00:36,290
Come on.

15
00:00:36,290 --> 00:00:38,250
You're going to be late. Get going.

16
00:00:38,250 --> 00:00:39,660
Aw, come on.

17
00:00:43,290 --> 00:00:45,960
Well, I'm heading out.

18
00:00:45,960 --> 00:00:47,380
Have a good day.

19
00:00:53,180 --> 00:00:55,100
Geez,
look at that huge grin.

20
00:00:55,310 --> 00:00:56,890
(Manager)

21
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,890
Hmm?

22
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,980
Hello, Shiono-san.

23
00:01:00,980 --> 00:01:02,230
It's my day off today.

24
00:01:02,230 --> 00:01:03,650
Sorry to bother you so early.

25
00:01:03,650 --> 00:01:05,570
But I thought I should let you know as soon as possible.

26
00:01:05,570 --> 00:01:07,900
What's wrong?
Did something happen?

27
00:01:07,900 --> 00:01:10,150
About the model gig for that magazine
we talked about...

28
00:01:10,150 --> 00:01:12,200
You got the job!

29
00:01:12,200 --> 00:01:13,780
What?!
